{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"4972f467b2939bc413933af8b33cdd2c\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\">call 表现出的特性，我们首先至少能想到以下两点：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"6a929125424168bffe99f80e69037207\"><span class=\"ne-text\">call 是可以被所有的函数继承的，所以 call 方法应该被定义在 Function.prototype 上</span></li><li id=\"6efeb7bb87d1bf2e5e11eb6ddc7ca335\"><span class=\"ne-text\">call 方法做了两件事：</span></li></ul><ol ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"63abc5b18b249d9575f47683e5900853\"><span class=\"ne-text\">改变 this 的指向，将 this 绑到第一个入参指定的的对象上去；</span></li><li id=\"37e8aecd2e4030cbc11c70c842ab8975\"><span class=\"ne-text\">根据输入的参数，执行函数。</span></li></ol><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"vp6tn\" class=\"ne-codeblock\">Function.prototype.myCall = function(context,...args){\n \t\t// step1: 把函数挂到目标对象上（这里的 this 就是我们要改造的那个函数）\n    context.func = this\n    // step2: 执行函数，利用扩展运算符将数组展开\n    context.func(...args)\n    // step3: 删除 step1 中挂到目标对象上的函数，把目标对象”完璧归赵”\n    delete context.func\n}\n\nFunction.prototype.myApply = function (context, args) {\n  context.func = this;\n  context.func(...args);\n  delete context.func;\n};\n\n\nFunction.prototype.myBind = function (context, ...args) {\n  let that = this;\n  return function () {\n    context.func = that;\n    context.func(args);\n    delete context.func;\n  };\n};\n\n</pre><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"jz7Km\" class=\"ne-codeblock\">Function.prototype.myApply = function (context, arr) {\n  context.func = this;\n  let result;\n  if (!arr) {\n    result = context.func();\n  } else {\n    result = context.func(arr);\n  }\n  delete context.func;\n  return result;\n};\n\nFunction.prototype.myBind = function (ctx, ...args) {\n  let self = this;\n  return function () {\n    self.call(ctx, ...args);\n  };\n};</pre><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"nwoP6\" class=\"ne-codeblock\">var me = {\n\tname: 'sugar'\n}\n\nfunction showFullName(...surName) {\n\tconsole.log(`${this.name} ${surName}`)\n}\n\nshowFullName.myCall(me, 'call','radish') // sugar, call,radish \nshowFullName.myApply(me, ['apply','radish'])// sugar, apply, radish\nshowFullName.myBind(me, 'bind','radish')()// sugar, bind, radish</pre></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><p data-lake-id=\"4972f467b2939bc413933af8b33cdd2c\" id=\"4972f467b2939bc413933af8b33cdd2c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u981a8630\" id=\"u981a8630\">call 表现出的特性，我们首先至少能想到以下两点：</span></p><ul list=\"uc25210d9\"><li fid=\"udae7dbd3\" data-lake-id=\"6a929125424168bffe99f80e69037207\" id=\"6a929125424168bffe99f80e69037207\"><span data-lake-id=\"udf6b2c45\" id=\"udf6b2c45\">call 是可以被所有的函数继承的，所以 call 方法应该被定义在 Function.prototype 上</span></li><li fid=\"udae7dbd3\" data-lake-id=\"6efeb7bb87d1bf2e5e11eb6ddc7ca335\" id=\"6efeb7bb87d1bf2e5e11eb6ddc7ca335\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9b362260\" id=\"u9b362260\">call 方法做了两件事：</span></li></ul><ol list=\"u6e865f82\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"uef4465fa\" data-lake-id=\"63abc5b18b249d9575f47683e5900853\" id=\"63abc5b18b249d9575f47683e5900853\"><span data-lake-id=\"udda1059e\" id=\"udda1059e\">改变 this 的指向，将 this 绑到第一个入参指定的的对象上去；</span></li><li fid=\"uef4465fa\" data-lake-id=\"37e8aecd2e4030cbc11c70c842ab8975\" id=\"37e8aecd2e4030cbc11c70c842ab8975\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1365071e\" id=\"u1365071e\">根据输入的参数，执行函数。</span></li></ol><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22Function.prototype.myCall%20%3D%20function(context%2C...args)%7B%5Cn%20%5Ct%5Ct%2F%2F%20step1%3A%20%E6%8A%8A%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%8C%82%E5%88%B0%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%88%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%20this%20%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%82%A3%E4%B8%AA%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%89%5Cn%20%20%20%20context.func%20%3D%20this%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20step2%3A%20%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%E5%B0%86%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80%5Cn%20%20%20%20context.func(...args)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20step3%3A%20%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%20step1%20%E4%B8%AD%E6%8C%82%E5%88%B0%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%8A%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E2%80%9D%E5%AE%8C%E7%92%A7%E5%BD%92%E8%B5%B5%E2%80%9D%5Cn%20%20%20%20delete%20context.func%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5CnFunction.prototype.myApply%20%3D%20function%20(context%2C%20args)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20context.func%20%3D%20this%3B%5Cn%20%20context.func(...args)%3B%5Cn%20%20delete%20context.func%3B%5Cn%7D%3B%5Cn%5Cn%5CnFunction.prototype.myBind%20%3D%20function%20(context%2C%20...args)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20let%20that%20%3D%20this%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20function%20()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20context.func%20%3D%20that%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20context.func(args)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20delete%20context.func%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%3B%5Cn%7D%3B%5Cn%5Cn%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22theme%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22vp6tn%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22Function.prototype.myApply%20%3D%20function%20(context%2C%20arr)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20context.func%20%3D%20this%3B%5Cn%20%20let%20result%3B%5Cn%20%20if%20(!arr)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20result%20%3D%20context.func()%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%20else%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20result%20%3D%20context.func(arr)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20delete%20context.func%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20result%3B%5Cn%7D%3B%5Cn%5CnFunction.prototype.myBind%20%3D%20function%20(ctx%2C%20...args)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20let%20self%20%3D%20this%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20function%20()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20self.call(ctx%2C%20...args)%3B%5Cn%20%20%7D%3B%5Cn%7D%3B%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22theme%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22jz7Km%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22var%20me%20%3D%20%7B%5Cn%5Ctname%3A%20'sugar'%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cnfunction%20showFullName(...surName)%20%7B%5Cn%5Ctconsole.log(%60%24%7Bthis.name%7D%20%24%7BsurName%7D%60)%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5CnshowFullName.myCall(me%2C%20'call'%2C'radish')%20%2F%2F%20sugar%2C%20call%2Cradish%20%5CnshowFullName.myApply(me%2C%20%5B'apply'%2C'radish'%5D)%2F%2F%20sugar%2C%20apply%2C%20radish%5CnshowFullName.myBind(me%2C%20'bind'%2C'radish')()%2F%2F%20sugar%2C%20bind%2C%20radish%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22theme%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22nwoP6%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"4972f467b2939bc413933af8b33cdd2c\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span class=\"ne-text\">call 表现出的特性，我们首先至少能想到以下两点：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"6a929125424168bffe99f80e69037207\"><span class=\"ne-text\">call 是可以被所有的函数继承的，所以 call 方法应该被定义在 Function.prototype 上</span></li><li id=\"6efeb7bb87d1bf2e5e11eb6ddc7ca335\"><span class=\"ne-text\">call 方法做了两件事：</span></li></ul><ol ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"63abc5b18b249d9575f47683e5900853\"><span class=\"ne-text\">改变 this 的指向，将 this 绑到第一个入参指定的的对象上去；</span></li><li id=\"37e8aecd2e4030cbc11c70c842ab8975\"><span class=\"ne-text\">根据输入的参数，执行函数。</span></li></ol><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"vp6tn\" class=\"ne-codeblock\">Function.prototype.myCall = function(context,...args){\n \t\t// step1: 把函数挂到目标对象上（这里的 this 就是我们要改造的那个函数）\n    context.func = this\n    // step2: 执行函数，利用扩展运算符将数组展开\n    context.func(...args)\n    // step3: 删除 step1 中挂到目标对象上的函数，把目标对象”完璧归赵”\n    delete context.func\n}\n\nFunction.prototype.myApply = function (context, args) {\n  context.func = this;\n  context.func(...args);\n  delete context.func;\n};\n\n\nFunction.prototype.myBind = function (context, ...args) {\n  let that = this;\n  return function () {\n    context.func = that;\n    context.func(args);\n    delete context.func;\n  };\n};\n\n</pre><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"jz7Km\" class=\"ne-codeblock\">Function.prototype.myApply = function (context, arr) {\n  context.func = this;\n  let result;\n  if (!arr) {\n    result = context.func();\n  } else {\n    result = context.func(arr);\n  }\n  delete context.func;\n  return result;\n};\n\nFunction.prototype.myBind = function (ctx, ...args) {\n  let self = this;\n  return function () {\n    self.call(ctx, ...args);\n  };\n};</pre><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"nwoP6\" class=\"ne-codeblock\">var me = {\n\tname: 'sugar'\n}\n\nfunction showFullName(...surName) {\n\tconsole.log(`${this.name} ${surName}`)\n}\n\nshowFullName.myCall(me, 'call','radish') // sugar, call,radish \nshowFullName.myApply(me, ['apply','radish'])// sugar, apply, radish\nshowFullName.myBind(me, 'bind','radish')()// sugar, bind, radish</pre></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><p data-lake-id=\"4972f467b2939bc413933af8b33cdd2c\" id=\"4972f467b2939bc413933af8b33cdd2c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u981a8630\" id=\"u981a8630\">call 表现出的特性，我们首先至少能想到以下两点：</span></p><ul list=\"uc25210d9\"><li fid=\"udae7dbd3\" data-lake-id=\"6a929125424168bffe99f80e69037207\" id=\"6a929125424168bffe99f80e69037207\"><span data-lake-id=\"udf6b2c45\" id=\"udf6b2c45\">call 是可以被所有的函数继承的，所以 call 方法应该被定义在 Function.prototype 上</span></li><li fid=\"udae7dbd3\" data-lake-id=\"6efeb7bb87d1bf2e5e11eb6ddc7ca335\" id=\"6efeb7bb87d1bf2e5e11eb6ddc7ca335\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9b362260\" id=\"u9b362260\">call 方法做了两件事：</span></li></ul><ol list=\"u6e865f82\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"uef4465fa\" data-lake-id=\"63abc5b18b249d9575f47683e5900853\" id=\"63abc5b18b249d9575f47683e5900853\"><span data-lake-id=\"udda1059e\" id=\"udda1059e\">改变 this 的指向，将 this 绑到第一个入参指定的的对象上去；</span></li><li fid=\"uef4465fa\" data-lake-id=\"37e8aecd2e4030cbc11c70c842ab8975\" id=\"37e8aecd2e4030cbc11c70c842ab8975\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1365071e\" id=\"u1365071e\">根据输入的参数，执行函数。</span></li></ol><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22Function.prototype.myCall%20%3D%20function(context%2C...args)%7B%5Cn%20%5Ct%5Ct%2F%2F%20step1%3A%20%E6%8A%8A%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%8C%82%E5%88%B0%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%88%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%20this%20%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%82%A3%E4%B8%AA%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%89%5Cn%20%20%20%20context.func%20%3D%20this%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20step2%3A%20%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%E5%B0%86%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80%5Cn%20%20%20%20context.func(...args)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20step3%3A%20%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%20step1%20%E4%B8%AD%E6%8C%82%E5%88%B0%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%8A%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E2%80%9D%E5%AE%8C%E7%92%A7%E5%BD%92%E8%B5%B5%E2%80%9D%5Cn%20%20%20%20delete%20context.func%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5CnFunction.prototype.myApply%20%3D%20function%20(context%2C%20args)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20context.func%20%3D%20this%3B%5Cn%20%20context.func(...args)%3B%5Cn%20%20delete%20context.func%3B%5Cn%7D%3B%5Cn%5Cn%5CnFunction.prototype.myBind%20%3D%20function%20(context%2C%20...args)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20let%20that%20%3D%20this%3B%5Cn%20%20return%20function%20()%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20context.func%20%3D%20that%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20context.func(args)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20delete%20co